{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HdjG8c2GsVewYPsyzoBxKC","type":"tool_result","content":"open Matrix\n\nsection DotProduct\n\nvariable [Fintype m] [Fintype n]\n\n/-- `dotProduct v w` is the sum of the entrywise products `v i * w i`.\n\nSee also `dotProductEquiv`. -/\ndef dotProduct [Mul α] [AddCommMonoid α] (v w : m → α) : α :=\n  ∑ i, v i * w i\n\n/- The precedence of 72 comes immediately after ` • ` for `SMul.smul`,\nso that `r₁ • a ⬝ᵥ r₂ • b` is parsed as `(r₁ • a) ⬝ᵥ (r₂ • b)` here. -/\n@[inherit_doc]\ninfixl:72 \" ⬝ᵥ \" => dotProduct\n\ntheorem dotProduct_assoc [NonUnitalSemiring α] (u : m → α) (w : n → α) (v : Matrix m n α) :\n    (fun j => u ⬝ᵥ fun i => v i j) ⬝ᵥ w = u ⬝ᵥ fun i => v i ⬝ᵥ w := by\n  simpa [dotProduct, Finset.mul_sum, Finset.sum_mul, mul_assoc] using Finset.sum_comm","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6cd06645-8a00-4465-88a4-569f84504161","uuid":"98ec1ff0-6fd9-4169-8deb-60b086482c68","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"open Matrix\n\nsection DotProduct\n\nvariable [Fintype m] [Fintype n]\n\n/-- `dotProduct v w` is the sum of the entrywise products `v i * w i`.\n\nSee also `dotProductEquiv`. -/\ndef dotProduct [Mul α] [AddCommMonoid α] (v w : m → α) : α :=\n  ∑ i, v i * w i\n\n/- The precedence of 72 comes immediately after ` • ` for `SMul.smul`,\nso that `r₁ • a ⬝ᵥ r₂ • b` is parsed as `(r₁ • a) ⬝ᵥ (r₂ • b)` here. -/\n@[inherit_doc]\ninfixl:72 \" ⬝ᵥ \" => dotProduct\n\ntheorem dotProduct_assoc [NonUnitalSemiring α] (u : m → α) (w : n → α) (v : Matrix m n α) :\n    (fun j => u ⬝ᵥ fun i => v i j) ⬝ᵥ w = u ⬝ᵥ fun i => v i ⬝ᵥ w := by\n  simpa [dotProduct, Finset.mul_sum, Finset.sum_mul, mul_assoc] using Finset.sum_comm","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
